	Pitt shoes    
	 London, Sept. 22 (PTI): Brad Pitt has taken the latest Hollywood fad for monograms to the next level with shoes bearing his initials.      
	While celebrities have till now monogrammed cars and homes, Pitt looked intent on making a style statement with the shoes. He stepped out wearing black shoes with his initials BP engraved on them in yellow.
                                                                                                                                                                       
